  "description": "NLP extraction-pipeline health (S6) — relation precision-gate drops (Loki), model fallback engagement (Prometheus + Loki), and extraction API error/latency (Prometheus). NOTE: the Prometheus ml_api_* series (nlp_pipeline_*) only populate once the DeepSeekExtractionAdapter in article_consumer_main.py is constructed with metrics=create_ml_metrics(...). See dashboard text panel.",
  "editable": true,
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "graphTooltip": 1,
  "id": null,
  "links": [],
  "panels": [
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "datasource",
        "uid": "grafana"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "id": 100,
      "options": {
        "code": {
          "language": "plaintext",
          "showLineNumbers": false,
          "showMiniMap": false
        },
        "content": "## Extraction-Pipeline Health (S6 / nlp-pipeline)\n\n**Signal 1 — Precision-gate drops** (rows 1–2): sourced from the structured log event `deep_extraction.relations_filtered` via **Loki**. Emitted by the article-consumer when `relation_validation.validate_relations()` drops structurally-invalid relations.\n\n**Signals 2 & 3 — Fallback / error / latency** (rows 3–5): sourced from **Prometheus** `nlp_pipeline_ml_api_requests_total{operation=\"extract\"}` and `nlp_pipeline_ml_api_latency_seconds{operation=\"extract\"}`. ⚠️ These series are currently EMPTY: `DeepSeekExtractionAdapter` in `article_consumer_main.py` is built without `metrics=`, so `self._metrics is None` and no extract metric is ever emitted. The Loki fallback panel (row 3, right) works today.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "11.6.0",
      "title": "",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "loki"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          },
          "unit": "short",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "bars",
            "fillOpacity": 60,
            "stacking": {
              "mode": "normal",
              "group": "A"
            }
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 4
      },
      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "calcs": [
            "sum"
          ],
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "right"
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi",
          "sort": "desc"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "loki",
            "uid": "loki"
          },
          "expr": "sum(sum_over_time({service_name=~\"nlp-pipeline-article-consumer.*\"} | json | event=`deep_extraction.relations_filtered` | unwrap dropped_self_loop [$__auto]))",
          "legendFormat": "self_loop",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "loki",
            "uid": "loki"
          },
          "expr": "sum(sum_over_time({service_name=~\"nlp-pipeline-article-consumer.*\"} | json | event=`deep_extraction.relations_filtered` | unwrap dropped_oov_predicate [$__auto]))",
          "legendFormat": "oov_predicate",
          "refId": "B"
        },
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "loki",
            "uid": "loki"
          },
          "expr": "sum(sum_over_time({service_name=~\"nlp-pipeline-article-consumer.*\"} | json | event=`deep_extraction.relations_filtered` | unwrap dropped_common_noun_endpoint [$__auto]))",
          "legendFormat": "common_noun_endpoint",
          "refId": "C"
        },
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "loki",
            "uid": "loki"
          },
          "expr": "sum(sum_over_time({service_name=~\"nlp-pipeline-article-consumer.*\"} | json | event=`deep_extraction.relations_filtered` | unwrap dropped_invalid_listed_on [$__auto]))",
          "legendFormat": "invalid_listed_on",
          "refId": "D"
        },
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "loki",
            "uid": "loki"
          },
          "expr": "sum(sum_over_time({service_name=~\"nlp-pipeline-article-consumer.*\"} | json | event=`deep_extraction.relations_filtered` | unwrap dropped_empty_field [$__auto]))",
          "legendFormat": "empty_field",
          "refId": "E"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Relations Dropped by Gate Reason (Loki)",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "loki"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "unit": "percentunit",
          "min": 0,
          "max": 1,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "yellow",
                "value": 0.2
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 0.5
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 4
      },
      "id": 2,
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto",
        "orientation": "auto",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "textMode": "auto"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "loki",
            "uid": "loki"
          },
          "expr": "sum(sum_over_time({service_name=~\"nlp-pipeline-article-consumer.*\"} | json | event=`deep_extraction.relations_filtered` | unwrap dropped_total [$__range])) / (sum(sum_over_time({service_name=~\"nlp-pipeline-article-consumer.*\"} | json | event=`deep_extraction.relations_filtered` | unwrap dropped_total [$__range])) + sum(sum_over_time({service_name=~\"nlp-pipeline-article-consumer.*\"} | json | event=`deep_extraction.relations_filtered` | unwrap kept [$__range])))",
          "legendFormat": "drop rate",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Relation Drop Rate (dropped / (dropped+kept), selected range)",
      "type": "stat"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
